sequenceDiagram 
    participant U as User
    participant CF as CubeFactory (pure)
    participant KV as KVHub (state)
    participant TE as TrustEvaluator (pure)
    participant PE as PartialEngine (pure)
    participant IE as IntegrationEngine (pure)
    participant CE as ConflictEngine (pure)
    participant DE as DefragEngine (pure)

    U->>CF: Queryテキスト
    CF->>KV: QueryCubeをput

    KV->>TE: 全Cube + QueryCube
    TE->>KV: trustスコア

    KV->>PE: Top-k + trust
    PE->>PE: 部分回答生成

    PE->>CE: 葛藤度 + trust分布
    CE->>U: 採用/不採用/対立整理

    Note over KV,DE: Test5で発火
    KV->>DE: cluster履歴
    DE->>KV: 新Origin